# Per-test staging area created by otherTests/saw-core-lean/support/lean-{elaborate,proof,shape}-test.sh.
# Each test mkdirs intTestsProbe/<test-name>/, copies its emitted .lean in,
# elaborates with `lake env lean`, then rm -rf's the subdirectory. The
# parent intTestsProbe/ may be left on disk; nothing under it should
# ever be committed.
saw-core-lean/lean/intTestsProbe/
